    "98192647": {
      "title": "A vertical flat-bed discontinuous electrophoresis system in polyacrylamide gel",
      "abstract": "Abstract A technique for electrophoretic separations in flat-bed vertical discontinuous acrylamide gel systems is described. Comparisons of protein separations and esterase zymograms indicate that greater resolution is achieved with this procedure than with previously reported systems. With schlieren optics, migration rates and zone diffusion may be studied during separation in this system. The accurate location of well-resolved protein zones by optical or staining procedures provides a small-scale highresolution preparative capability in addition to the qualitative and quantitative employment of this system."
